00:19:37.198 --> 00:19:38.740
fix a computer or
anything like that.

00:19:38.740 --> 00:19:40.740
- That's not necessarily
boy stuff, though.

00:19:40.740 --> 00:19:41.990
- This is how I'm comfortable.

00:19:41.990 --> 00:19:44.620
I'd rather not wear baggy
clothes and backwards hats

00:19:44.620 --> 00:19:47.530
and polo shirts.

00:19:47.530 --> 00:19:48.250
That's me.

00:19:48.250 --> 00:19:50.650
This is how-- No
one criticizes me

00:19:50.650 --> 00:19:54.130
for the way I dress because
I pass for what feminine

00:19:54.130 --> 00:19:55.385
is supposed to be.

00:19:55.385 --> 00:19:57.760
- There actually is a moment
