00:20:00.690 --> 00:20:03.190
like, knowing that he wanted
to be a woman because he wanted

00:20:03.190 --> 00:20:05.390
to like wear frilly
underwear and carry a purse.

00:20:05.390 --> 00:20:06.820
And I'm like, well, I'm
a woman and I've never

00:20:06.820 --> 00:20:08.820
worn frilly underwear and
